{"tid":188732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"會員9527~做打手咬熱狗都唔該專業好嗎？","createTime":"2017-04-06T01:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T23:30:56.000Z","uid":34884,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0b97d05cd76147b382a7af5212b1f19c5208ab","tid":188732,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"明明三個月前喺個post入面已經駁左佢『泰博Degree直上Phd』同『陳雲唔係中文系出身去Lingu中文系教』<br />\n隔左三個月搏人唔記得又loop過同一堆point<br />\n健吾傳理出身，吳偉明歷史系出身<br />\n依家兩個都喺中大日本研究系教書，依家吳偉明仲係dept head<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pkc4w0al\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpkc4w0al&h=bfbdb02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jo0pz3be\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjo0pz3be&h=c1ec1b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p21k8hx6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp21k8hx6&h=b1c0000d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8p735a9i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8p735a9i&h=02f8e0c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/c2oe6z9x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fc2oe6z9x&h=29b7ac2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9ao8v1sp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9ao8v1sp&h=d9c51506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最好笑係喺另一個post屈徐承恩係左膠專寫文攻擊本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地徐承恩係學者，有份寫民族論，港大幫成日share佢既post（除左叫梁游收皮嗰個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r52a91j4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr52a91j4&h=9ee2dc5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2zsmjtyg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2zsmjty