1e0c6865b9c3aecde97957877d48614e95732102","tid":188732,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:22:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>御理好慘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回流紅登又被紅登仔玩</span><br />\n係連登又被連登仔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇考慮縮回去係熱狗page<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅登CC台唔係熱狗地盤咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7360dc561881e022b93c5a431f23bc954db9d987","tid":188732,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>御理好慘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回流紅登又被紅登仔玩</span><br />\n係連登又被連登仔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇考慮縮回去係熱狗page<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅登CC台唔係熱狗地盤咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ff99ff93fb7b35291727048f7b229212a51b92","tid":188732,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2fd97e30c06278904f4efe4ef52eca689512286","tid":188732,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:24:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>熱狗屈人食熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n御理：我唔係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我只不過係睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恭喜發財，新年快樂！新年要講多啲好嘢，所以都要講下熱狗啲好嘢。<br />\n<br />\n《熱狗七大好嘢》<br />\n1）得道多助：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但凡熱狗有敵人、有危機，自然有班自稱唔係熱狗嘅人出嚟抱打不平，咁多志同道合，所以次次都唔關熱狗事。</span></span><br />\n2）始終如一：<br />\n偶像燒基本法，熱狗拍爛手掌，到偶像永續基本法，熱狗又係拍爛手掌，喺跟偶像拍子起舞呢方面，熱狗始終如一。<br />\n3）不拘小節：<br />\n義士蒙塵又好，因節目受傷又好，明知熱血時報過水濕腳抽相關人士三成都照課金，由此可知熱狗幾咁不拘小節。<br />\n4）勇於承擔：<br />\n平時點牙擦都好，上到法庭都會話好後悔自己嘅所作所為，承諾以後唔會再做，甚至從此歸隱。<br />\n5）能言善辯：<br />\n熱狗一出獨家辯論三寶：「東拉西扯」、「標籤」同「謾罵」，你想拗贏佢哋，真係談何容易。<br />\n6）武藝高強：<br />\n無論腿法（踢親建制網台記者），又或者兵器（玻璃樽扑街坊），熱狗都相當耍家，如果用嚟對付政權，仲唔搞到佢哋風聲鶴唳。<br />\n7）破舊立新：<br />\n喺熱狗大量使用下，短短日子就將「熱血」呢個詞嘅意思變成：冇原則、冇邏輯、搞破壞、搞批鬥、尊己卑人、諉過於人。"},{"pid":"40c97994d56b7a5a79a9f680454c8030981de958","tid":188732,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>御理好慘<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">回流紅登又被紅登仔玩</span><br />\n係連登又被連登仔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇考慮縮回去係熱狗page<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅登CC台唔係熱狗地盤咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見到連佐倉綾音都屌柒佢"},{"pid":"c16d217effd3431d112610eddfbf6da07382296b","tid":188732,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻熱狗柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />躝返紅燈同你班熱狗圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n御理<br />\n過連登被撚&gt;回流紅登想同熱狗圍爐被踢走&gt;又過連登被撚"},{"pid":"cb7381ba0dcef24dcbd152f4d27d2d95a1bc2f52","tid":188732,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"鬼作洪仔嗰班都唔妥御理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef6de2af29ca1d95584bcc1b82a8567af825980","tid":188732,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼作洪仔嗰班都唔妥御理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.